title: CSE: 2015-0803 - Name and Symbol Change - Asean Energy Corp. (ASA)
text:
August 19, 2015 15:28 ET CSE: 2015-0803 - Name and Symbol Change - Asean Energy Corp. (ASA) 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - Aug. 19, 2015) - Asean Energy Corp. (ASA) has announced a name change to Genovation Capital Corp. Shares will begin trading under the new name and symbol on August 20, 2015. 
Disclosure documents are available www.thecse.com Effective Date: August 20, 2015 New CUSIP: 372437103
